Optional after

after: string

Inherited from ListOptions.after

The ID of the item after which to retrieve the next page

Optional filter

filter: object

The device event filter

Constructed like so:

 filter: {
   deviceId: { $eq: "1" },
   eventDate: { $gte: new Date("01-01-2014"), $lte: new Date("01-01-2018") }
 }

Type declaration

  • Optional deviceId?: ComparisonObject<string>
  • Optional eventDate?: ComparisonObject<Date>
  • Optional type?: ComparisonObject<string>
